A cyberpunk scene showing a futuristic factory interior where translucent, glowing balloons in various neon colors (electric pink, cyan, purple) float upward from mechanical production pods. The balloons are semi-transparent, revealing swirling gas patterns inside them like contained galaxies. Industrial pipes and chrome machinery surround the scene, dripping with condensation and lit by harsh fluorescent strips. In the foreground, a robotic arm delicately releases a freshly-created balloon that reflects the ambient glow. The atmosphere is moody with volumetric fog, rain-slicked metal surfaces, and holographic control panels displaying abstract flowing diagrams. Deep shadows contrast with vibrant neon accents in teal and magenta.
